results.name: Basket Profi 'Mesa'
results.story: The adidas Basket Profi ‘Mesa’ updates the vintage hoops shoe with a stitched textile upper in a light brown hue. Tonal serrated three-stripes are joined by a circular adidas badge on the lateral ankle. A drawcord lacing system provides a secure fit, while a suede heel overlay offers added durability and support. The mid-top is mounted on a contrasting black rubber cupsole, featuring a grippy herringbone traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Swift Run X J 'Black Fluorescent Pop'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Swift Run X J ‘Black Fluorescent Pop’ treats the retro-inspired low-top to an essential black and white color scheme, enlivened with fluorescent pops of color on the eyelets and forefoot. An Ortholite sockliner combines with an EVA midsole to deliver soft cushioning with each step. Underfoot, a black rubber outsole is equipped with a series of flex grooves that accommodate the natural motion of the foot.

results.name: Pro Model 'White Gold Metallic'
results.story: The adidas Pro Model ‘White Gold Metallic’ gives the vintage hoops shoe a pristine makeover, featuring a white leather upper with gilded branding hits. They include ‘Pro Model’ stamped on the lateral quarter panel and adidas’ Trefoil logo on the navy heel tab. The latter hue is repeated on the collar lining and rubber outsole, equipped with a traditional herringbone tread for reliable traction. Heritage details include the iconic rubber shell toe and serrated leather three-stripes.

results.name: Wmns Superstar Boot 'Night Indigo'
results.story: The adidas women’s Superstar Boot ‘Night Indigo’ reimagines the vintage hoops shoe as a rugged outdoor boot. The monochromatic navy upper is constructed from lightweight nylon with tonal suede paneling at the heel and toe, the latter embellished with stitched lines that replicate the iconic shell toe of the original. The sneaker-boot hybrid is mounted on a black rubber sole unit, featuring a herringbone traction pattern for maximum grip.

results.name: adidas ZX 2K Phormar Craig Green Blue
results.story: The Craig Green x adidas ZX 2K Phormar ‘Blue’ brings the British fashion designer’s unrestrained aesthetic to the Three Stripes’ ZX running franchise. An exposed tension cord system adds structure to an upper built with semi-translucent nylon in a bold royal blue finish. A drawcord lacing system combines with a stretchy interior sleeve to deliver a snug, comfortable fit. The lightweight sneaker rides on a full-length Boost midsole, painted black and partially enclosed within a wraparound TPU cage.

results.name: Terrex Speed Pro Trail 'White Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Speed Pro Trail ‘White Solar Yellow’ carries a streamlined build that blends visibility and sustainability. Recycled materials are incorporated into a neon-tinged mesh upper, overlaid with abrasion-resistant overlays and accented with 3M reflective detailing. The low-top rides on a full-length Lightstrike midsole, marked with Terrex branding and finished in a black and white gradient finish. A lugged Continental rubber outsole provides sure footing on uneven terrain.

results.name: Adizero 11 Primeknit 'White Clear Grey'
results.story: The adidas Adizero 11 Primeknit ‘White Clear Grey’ delivers a blank-slate colorway of a lightweight football cleat built for speed on the gridiron. The upper is constructed from breathable white Primeknit, bolstered with a tonal TPU overlay for added support and durability. An elastic cuff is equipped with dual webbing pull tabs to assist with easy on and off. A Sprintframe outsole features a reinforced heel and strategically placed Sprintstuds for stop-and-go traction.

results.name: adidas Nizza Lo Wales Bonner Purple
Wmns Terrex Skychaser GTX 2.0 'Black Gum'
results.story: The adidas women’s Terrex Skychaser GTX 2.0 ‘Black Gum’ delivers a neutral colorway of a rugged hiking shoe built with sustainability in mind. Recycled materials are incorporated into a breathable textile upper lined with a waterproof Gore-Tex membrane. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length Boost midsole, reinforced with a stabilization frame and supported by a lugged Continental rubber outsole that offers reliable grip in all conditions.

results.name: Predator.1 Microbounce 'Demonskin - Black'
results.story: The adidas Predator.1 Microbounce ‘Black’ delivers a lifestyle silhouette that combines the brand’s retro cushioning technology with a Primeknit upper that recalls the Predator Freak.1 soccer cleat. In addition to the gradient finish and forefoot three-strip branding, the homage is made complete with a textured vamp that replicates the look of Demonskin. Springy cushioning comes courtesy of a Microbounce midsole, lifted straight from adidas’ early 2000s archive.

results.name: Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 J 'Grey Super Pop'
results.story: The adidas Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 J ‘Grey Super Pop’ makes use of a grey open-mesh upper with laceless slip-on construction, allowing little kids to easily slip on and off their shoes. Bright pink accents land on a webbing pull tab and an elastic midfoot strap marked with adidas branding. A second adidas wordmark is debossed on a stitched TPU heel patch. The casual sneaker rides on a plush Cloudfoam sole unit, good for lightweight cushioning with every step.

results.name: Solar Boost 3 'Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Solar Boost 3 ‘Solar Yellow’ wears a breathable engineered mesh upper in a neon hue. Reflective detailing on the sneaker’s signature three-stripes continues the hi-vis theme. A molded Control Rail reinforces the full-length Boost midsole, which works in tandem with adidas’ Linear Energy Push system for increased responsiveness and energy return. Underfoot, the Stretchweb outsole is built with Continental rubber for grippy traction.

results.name: Wmns Solar Boost 3 'Hi-Res Yellow'
results.story: The adidas women’s Solar Boost 3 ‘Hi-Res Yellow’ dresses the performance runner with a neon-colored engineered mesh upper, overlaid with seamless no-sew skins and reflective silver three-stripes. The seamless build is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, reinforced with a molded Contrail Rail for improved stability. In lieu of adidas’ standard Torsion bar, the shoe makes use of adidas’ Linear Energy Push system, which reduces forefoot flex for enhanced energy return.

results.name: Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 J 'Black Solar Red'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 J ‘Black Solar Red’ features convenient slip-on construction on a lightweight silhouette inspired by classic running shoes. Breathable black mesh is utilized on the upper, secured with an elastic midfoot strap marked with adidas branding in oversized orange lettering. The minimalist upper rests on a plush Cloudfoam sole unit in a contrasting white finish. Underfoot, a modified waffle tread delivers reliable grip.

results.name: Wmns Adilette Comfort Slide 'Clear Pink Leopard'
results.story: The adidas women’s Adilette Comfort Slide ‘Clear Pink Leopard’ combines elevated comfort with an eye-catching animal print. The upper takes the form of a wide synthetic-leather bandage strap, lined in soft textile and entirely covered in leopard spots. They’re joined by signature three-stripe branding in a pastel pink hue. A contrasting dark grey finish is applied to a lightweight Cloudfoam midsole, reinforced underfoot by a durable EVA outsole.

results.name: Wmns Solar Boost 3 'Black Screaming Pink'
results.story: The adidas women’s Solar Boost 3 ‘Black Screaming Pink’ features highlighter accents on a performance running shoe that delivers a responsive and stable ride. The upper is constructed from black engineered mesh with seamless fuchsia overlays and silver reflective three-stripes. A full-length Boost midsole is reinforced with a molded Control Rail and a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole. Increased energy return is provided by adidas’ Linear Energy Push system.

results.name: Solar Boost 3 'Grey Screaming Orange'
results.story: The adidas Solar Boost 3 ‘Grey Screaming Orange’ utilizes a breathable engineered mesh upper, finished in a neutral grey hue and accented with vibrant citrus accents. Reflective matte silver three-stripes adorn the sneaker’s perforated quarter panel. The performance runner sits atop a full-length Boost midsole, reinforced with a molded Control Rail for enhanced stability. Underfoot, adidas’ Linear Energy Push system offers torsional support and improved energy return.

results.name: Supernova+ 'Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Supernova+ ‘Solar Yellow’ applies a fluorescent hue to a performance running shoe designed for beginner and intermediate runners. 100% recycled polyester makes up the composition of the engineered mesh upper, featuring reflective details that include adidas’ signature three-stripe branding. The seamless upper is mounted on a lightweight Bounce midsole, supplemented with responsive Boost cushioning in the forefoot and heel.

results.name: Wmns Supernova+ 'White Silver Pink'
results.story: The adidas women’s Supernova+ ‘White Silver Pink’ offers seamless comfort via a one-piece mesh upper that wraps around the foot in breathable support. The sock-like build is energized by various candy-colored accents and shiny metallic silver overlays. They’re joined by reflective three-stripes in a matte grey finish. The running shoe’s hybrid tooling combines a full-length Bounce midsole with responsive Boost cushioning in the forefoot and heel.

results.name: Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 'Triple Black'
results.story: The adidas Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 ‘Triple Black’ showcases a stealthy one-note finish on a slip-on silhouette inspired by classic running style. 50% recycled content makes up the composition of the breathable mesh upper, equipped with a webbing pull tab at the heel for easy on and off. Tonal adidas branding adorns an elastic strap that offers midfoot lockdown. A plush Cloudfoam midsole maintains the sneaker’s monochromatic design theme.

results.name: Wmns Supernova+ 'Grey Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas women’s Supernova+ ‘Grey Solar Yellow’ offers a blend of soft and responsive cushioning, bundled in a neutral-colored package with hi-vis accents. They include reflective silver three-stripes and seamless neon overlays, which enliven an engineered mesh upper composed of 100% recycled polyester. The streamlined build rests on a cushy Bounce midsole, enhanced with visible Boost inserts nestled in the heel and forefoot.

results.name: Her Studio London x Wmns Adilette Slide 'Floral - White'
results.story: The Her Studio London x adidas women’s Adilette Slide ‘Floral’ dresses the versatile sandal in an ornate design, courtesy of the female-led print studio based in East London. A lush multicolor floral print decorates the wide bandage-strap upper, made with synthetic leather and accented with raised three-stripe branding. Dual adidas and Her Studio London branding is printed on a soft, contoured footbed that yields step-in comfort.

results.name: adidas Stan Smith OG Velcro Fairway Green
Forum 84 Low 'Orbit Grey'
results.story: The adidas Forum 84 Low ‘Orbit Grey’ highlights a subdued finish on a retro silhouette that embodies bulky ‘80s basketball style. Traditional laces combine with an adjustable ankle strap to secure an off-white leather upper accented with tonal hairy suede three-stripes. The low-top is mounted on a durable rubber cupsole with an exposed EVA wedge on the medial side. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a circular traction pattern and a contrasting red pivot point.

results.name: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Pearl
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 ‘Ash Pearl’ applies contrast color blocking to the re-engineered Primeknit upper. Most of the knit build features a blend of indigo, grey and navy fibers, while the top half of the sneaker’s lateral side is rendered in subtle cream and beige tones. The latter hue is repeated on the signature post-dyed monofilament side stripe. The lightweight sneaker is supported by a full-length Boost midsole, its sidewalls reinforced with an off-white rubber cage.

results.name: Pharrell x Crazy BYW 2.0 'Triple Black'
results.story: The Pharrell x adidas Crazy BYW 2.0 ‘Triple Black’ is drawn from a monochromatic collection that extends a creative partnership originally launched in 2014. The lightweight hoops shoe makes use of a breathable textile and mesh upper, fortified with tonal synthetic leather overlays and accented with a series of small triangles throughout — a nod to Pharrell’s signature Hu branding. Responsive cushioning arrives via a Boost midsole, painted black and reinforced with a herringbone rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Yeezy QNTM Sea Teal
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Quantum ‘Sea Teal’ dresses the lifestyle silhouette in a breathable knit upper that blends mostly neutral grey and black tones with washed-out teal accents. A soft elastic collar provides a comfortable fit around the ankle, while the seamless heel counter is designed to hug the back of the foot for enhanced containment. A semi-translucent rubber cage shores up the full-length Boost midsole, supported underfoot by a herringbone-traction gum rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Futurecraft 4D 2021 Black Green
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the adidas Futurecraft 4D ‘Core Black’ brings back the running shoe’s OG colorway from 2018. Breathable Primeknit is utilized on the upper, accented with reflective grey three-stripes and lined in textile for a comfortable, sock-like fit. The lightweight build is mounted on adidas’ innovative 4D midsole, delivering finely tuned cushioning based on 17 years of running data. Finished in a Linen Green hue, the lattice structure is developed using a blend of light, oxygen and liquid resin.

results.name: Top Ten Low RB 'Black Royal Blue'
adidas Forum Low Bad Bunny
results.story: Kicking off a creative partnership between the chart-topping reggaeton artist and the German sportswear brand, the Bad Bunny x adidas Forum Buckle Low ‘The First Café’ gives the nod to the morning cup of coffee that starts the musician’s daily routine. Varying mocha hues are applied to the leather and suede upper, secured with traditional lacing, a bungee cord around the heel and an adjustable midfoot strap with buckle closure. The kicks come with a removable second tongue and extra laces in aqua and lime green.

results.name: Disney x Superstar 360 X Infant 'Minnie Mouse'
Disney x Superstar 360 X Infant 'Minnie Mouse Bow'
adidas Samba ADV Maite Steenhoudt
results.story: Designed in collaboration with the brand’s team rider, the Maité Steenhoudt x adidas Samba ADV ‘Black White’ delivers a skate-ready version of the iconic silhouette. Hairy black suede is utilized on the upper, contrasted by off-white suede detailing in the same hairy texture. The tonal coating on the signature T-toe overlay is designed to eventually wear away, reveal a contrasting red finish underneath. ‘Samba’ is handwritten on the lateral quarter panel of the right shoe, while ‘Maité’ is scrawled on the left. The skater’s illustrated likeness adorns the tongue tag.

results.name: adidas Gazelle ADV Nora Vasconcellos
results.story: Reimagined for skateboarding, the Nora Vasconcellos x adidas Gazelle ADV ‘White Soft Vision’ is designed in collaboration with the Three Stripes’ team rider. The white leather upper is reinforced with tonal suede detailing on the T-toe overlay and heel tab, embellished with Nora’s custom artwork for a personal touch. Additional details include lavender three-stripes, an exposed foam tongue, and the skater’s first and middle names stamped in gold on the lateral heel of the left and right shoe, respectively.

results.name: adidas Yeezy 380 Covellite (Infants)
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Infants ‘Covellite’ offers sock-like comfort for growing feet. Finished in varying blue shades, the re-engineered Primeknit upper is equipped with no-tie stretch laces for easy on and off. A translucent monofilament window is woven directly into the knit construction for textural depth and added breathability. The sneaker sits atop a full-length Boost midsole, reinforced with wrapped sidewalls and a herringbone-tread gum rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Yeezy 380 Covellite (Kids)
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Kids ‘Covellite’ gets its name from a blue mineral composed of sulfide copper. Like its inspiration, the shoe features an exterior surface finished in a craggy texture and varying blue shades. The re-engineered Primeknit upper is accented with decorative no-tie stretch laces and a translucent monofilament window woven into the side panel. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a wrapped Boost midsole, supported underfoot by a herringbone tread gum rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Stan Smith Primegreen Collegiate Green
adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Covellite
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 ‘Covellite’ showcases a mix of navy, indigo, and grey tones throughout the re-engineered Primeknit upper. The camo-like design is punctuated by perforated detailing that accompanies the sneaker’s semi-translucent monofilament window, woven into the side panel to enhance the breathability of the sock-like build. Responsive cushioning arrives via a caged full-length Boost midsole, featuring a stacked, elevated heel and supported underfoot by a herringbone rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas NMD R1 Collegiate Green
results.story: The adidas NMD_R1 ‘Collegiate Green’ delivers a verdant colorway of the lifestyle runner that combines a sock-like fit with responsive cushioning. The knit textile upper is finished in a lush green hue and accented with contrasting white branding elements, including printed three-stripes and a 3D Trefoil logo on the molded heel patch. The sneaker rides on a standard white Boost midsole, equipped with tonal EVA plugs and reinforced by a gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Her Studio London x Wmns NMD_R1 'Floral - White'
results.story: Developed in partnership with the female-led design agency, the Her Studio London x adidas women’s NMD_R1 ‘Floral’ pairs cushioned comfort with lush graphics. They take the form of a multicolor floral print on the sneaker’s signature three-stripes and molded heel patch, allowing the details to stand out against a stark white textile backdrop. The blossoms make a repeat appearance on the NMD’s trademark EVA plug, embedded in the lateral sidewall of the Boost midsole.

results.name: Terrex Trailmaker J 'White Teal'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the adidas Terrex Trailmaker J ‘White Teal’ highlights candy-bright hues on a rugged trail shoe designed for outdoor adventures. Breathable white mesh is utilized on the upper, secured with an adjustable strap and rope laces integrated into the midfoot cage. A welded TPU mudguard wraps around the forefoot for added durability. Neon yellow coloring stands out on the full-length EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a lugged Traxion outsole made with grippy Continental rubber.

results.name: Wmns Adilette Slide 'White Light Purple Copper'
Wmns Forum Low 'I Love Dance - Frozen Green Pink'
Wmns NMD_R1 'Light Purple'
results.story: The adidas women’s NMD_R1 ‘Light Purple’ showcases a pastel finish throughout the knit textile upper, engineered to hug the foot in flexible, breathable support. Tonal three-stripes are accompanied by Trefoil branding hits at the tongue and molded heel patch. The lightweight build is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, fitted with signature EVA plugs that maintain the sneaker’s two-tone color scheme. A semi-translucent rubber outsole provides grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: adidas Forum Low I Love Dance (W)
Her Studio London x Wmns Nizza Platform 'Floral'
results.story: The Her Studio London x adidas women’s Nizza Platform ‘Floral’ is drawn from a footwear and apparel collection developed jointly with the print design agency based in East London. Their take on the vintage silhouette features a hectic floral print throughout the lightweight textile upper, accented with contrasting white three-stripes and mounted on a platform vulcanized rubber midsole. ‘Her Studio London’ is inscribed on an EVA sockliner that delivers lightweight cushioning with every step.

results.name: Her Studio London x Wmns Superstar Bold 'Floral'
results.story: Dropping as part of a larger collection with the print design agency, the Her Studio London x adidas women’s Superstar Bold ‘Floral’ treats the shell-toed sneaker to a stylish makeover. Pristine white leather is utilized on the upper, accented with shimmering metallic gold three-stripes and a baroque multicolor floral print on the enlarged heel tab. The low-top sits on a platform sole, complete with an exaggerated herringbone tread on the rubber outsole.

results.name: N3xt L3v3l Futurenatural 'Team Solar Green'
results.colorway: Team Solar Green/Team Solar Green/Cloud White

results.name: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 V2 Cream
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 V2 ‘Cream’ delivers an unassuming colorway of Kanye West’s running-inspired silhouette. The upper features rolled knit construction in a pale grey hue, reinforced with tonal no-sew skins and tan nubuck overlays. An off-white finish distinguishes the exaggerated EVA midsole, featuring sculpted sidewalls that conceal a full-length drop-in Boost unit. Underfoot, the rubber outsole uses a classic herringbone traction pattern for superior grip.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost 5.0 DNA Triple White (W)
Egle Zvirblyte x Wmns UltraBoost S&L DNA 'Setsubun'
results.story: Releasing as part of a footwear and apparel collection with the award-winning artist, the Egle Zvirblyte x adidas women’s UltraBoost S&L DNA ‘Setsubun’ updates the lifestyle runner with bold splashes of primary color. They enliven the molded midfoot cage, which bolsters a sock-like Primeknit upper made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic and zero virgin polyester. The sneaker’s full-length Boost midsole is supported underfoot by adidas’ Torsion bar and a grippy Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: Stella McCartney x Wmns UltraBoost 21 'White Black'
UltraBoost DNA CC_1 'White Screaming Orange'
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost DNA CC_1 ‘White Screaming Orange’ combines responsive cushioning with a breezy build inspired by the brand’s cult-favorite Climacool models. A layered RPU cage with cooling air channels bolsters the Primeknit upper, partially made with recycled materials and featuring UV reactive technology, which yields different colors when exposed to sunlight. The sneaker rides on a full-length Boost midsole, supported underfoot by a tri-tone Continental rubber outsole.
